## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of recent and comprehensive data on the sincerity of companies in aligning their missions and visions with actions. The findings are based on a selection of articles and may not represent the full spectrum of corporate practices globally. Additionally, the subjective nature of assessing "sincerity" can lead to varied interpretations and conclusions.

